title: Wraths Range 2nd Runescape Pk Video
description:
This is the second pk video from the famous Runescape video editor, Wraths Range.

This video was Wrath&#039;s last serious personal effort before launching into projects for other players such as Pixel Pirates and Jojo.

In this video Wrath&#039;s Range is a range pure with a mid 70s combat level. His range and magic are both 90+, and he uses barrage as well and launches impressive magic shortbow specs. I should add that this video is either early &#039;07, if not late &#039;06 -- so don&#039;t expect any fancy weapons/loot.

The kills/loot are not amazing, but in my opinion this is one of the last tastefully edited Runescape pk videos.

Seeded by Doodlepieguy. You may contact me via PM on Runevillage forums under the user name &#039;Doodle&#039;.
